comment._content: Accompanying note: "[Enrollees] in the current practical nursing class at Lincoln High School are shown, First row, left to right, Mrs. Julia Davis, Miss Betty Simmons, Miss Emily Bennett, Mrs. Verdelle Jefferson and Mrs. M.
